## Credentials

Your auth token, agent id, and project id live in this exact JSON file (you wrote it
during startup from the provisioning message):

```
{{ credential_path }}
```

If it is missing, re-read the latest Mission Control provisioning message — it contains
the exact JSON to write back to that path.

## Calling the Mission Control API

There is ONE guide for every API call: the **mission-control skill** at

```
skills/mission-control/SKILL.md
```

Read it and follow its two steps (read the credential file, then run `curl` with the
values written straight into the command). Do **not** invent your own command shapes,
build shell variables, or copy commands from other markdown files — the skill is the
source of truth.

`references/api_schema.md` (next to the skill) lists every endpoint for your role.
